      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to turn heads with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in truly mint condition, looking and driving as if it just left the showroom for the first time. Every detail, from the flawless paint to the spotless interior, has been meticulously maintained, making it a rare find for any serious buyer who demands perfection.",
